      "B_{\\mathrm{total}}(r,t) = B_{\\mathrm{dip}}(r;\\mu_{1}(t),r_{1}) + B_{\\mathrm{dip}}(r;\\mu_{2}(t),r_{2}) + B_{\\mathrm{constraint}}(r,t).",
